The way Google maps displaying is not there
Pls don't be confused after Chaitanya Puri Police station there's a gate  under which a huge construction project is going on, go inside the gate and turn to right this masjid is having a small minarate (minar)

Google PE ghalat rasta bata Raha hai confuse mat ho
Chaitanya Puri Police station k bazu hi ek gate hai jis k andar ek bahot bada construction ka kaam chal Raha hai bulidings ka, wo gate ka andar Jane k baad right mein ek rasta masjid ko ja Raha hai masjid ka ek chota minar hai zara ghor karein

featured_reviews.review_id:
This Masjid Name can Confuse anyone but this ''Mandi Masjid'' Actually it's located in Fruit Mandi just stands near on the main road, so it's called Mandi Masjid but it's not so clean place around the masjid, mostly this Masjid is occupied by the local sellers operates in fruit Mandi and less of outsiders, this is Masjid has all eminites, Wajooh Khana, and other needed amenities.
Please any one is around to this have a visit.
